{"tid":1018339,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英廉航轉降只因沒熱水沖咖啡 乘客譙：下次找別的理由","createTime":"2019-02-12T07:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T09:08:02.000Z","uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"896aabb2cea8731fb5c914768dfb9293063676e4","tid":1018339,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"英國廉航Jet2一架航班10日原訂飛往西班牙特內里費島（Tenerife），但因為機上沒有熱水，無法沖泡咖啡或茶，導致飛機被迫改降至曼徹斯特，讓多名乘客直接傻眼。<br />\n英國太陽報（The Sun）報導，這架編號LS155的航班原訂10日早上8時55分由蘇格蘭格拉斯哥（Glasgow）飛往特內里費島，但在飛越愛爾蘭的科克市（Cork）時臨時改降於曼徹斯特機場，原因為機上幫浦出現問題。<br />\nJet2發言人解釋，該航班轉降由於未能提供熱水沖製咖啡和茶，乘客已在曼徹斯特機場轉乘另一架飛機前往特內里費島。<br />\n不少乘客氣得在推特上大罵荒謬，有網友說，「Jet2下次找個好一點的理由吧！」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/12/realtime/5913397.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F12%2Frealtime%2F5913397.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=db0553b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國廉航Jet2一架航班10日原訂飛往西班牙特內里費島，但因為機上沒有熱水，無法沖泡咖啡或茶，導致飛機被迫改降曼徹斯特。取自太陽報<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3639220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F3639220&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuridffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=d11af3cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3639220</a>"},{"pid":"ac3671e7017636a3483024a435ef57a21be14a43","tid":1018339,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T07:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa28102c645e43211458299308517757e75ce40","tid":1018339,"uid":6063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:08:38.000Z","msg":"服務認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4054dfc7c5224d55be9161e7d2ebe1536e062a4e","tid":1018339